New algorithm description: The new algorithm calculates the score for each bin as the ratio of the rest capacity of the bin to the maximum capacity of the bin, divided by the sum of these ratios. Then, it normalizes the scores to ensure they sum up to 1.

Code:
code:
import numpy as np

def score(item: int, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    rest_capacity = max_capacity - bins
    scores = rest_capacity / max_capacity
    scores /= np.sum(scores)
    return scores
